  m_Name: dr-sturgeon-day2
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  characterName: Dr. Sturgeon
  characterPortrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 3cadb61783a8ad44abb478954be17e5d, type: 3}
  lines:
  - GOD THAT ASS DON'T LIE!
  - You remind me of my sister.
  - Congrats. Your second day here.
  - Between me and you, I look forward to the day you can't make that quota.
  - Anyway, I heard Perch didn't like the look of that handsome face.
  - No wonder he needs you to give him those eye balls. Maybe he is looking for ones
    that actually work.
  - Oh you didn't know? Give Perch eye balls you find and he will upgrade your rod.
  - Speaking of rods, I would give an arm and a leg to get a good look at yours.
  - And I am not talking about fishing.
  textSpeed: 30
  typingSound: {fileID: 8300000, guid: f5d143911732a1f43b570748ed2458a4, type: 3}
